Scala - Scalable Language 
  Statically typed - type checking at compile time
  Runs on JVM , fully inter operable with Java ie Scala code in Java and Java code in scala
  Both Procedural and object oriented
  It is a compiled language
SBT - Scala Build tool 
  -open source tool for scala and Java projects to compile , run ,test and package your project
  Why SBT?
  Native support for compiling Scala code
  Uses Apache Ivy for dependency management ie it also can support Maven format repositries
  Only update on request model
  Launch REPL ( Read - Eval - Print Loop ) -helps in checking small functionality
  
  
  
  
